This page will display the movie info stored in database and buttons that allow a user to score it. 

<% if @movie_search == nil %>
  <%= @new_movie.title %>
  <%= @new_movie.image_name %>
<% else %>
  <%= @movie_search.title %>
  <%= @movie_search.image_name %>
<% end %>

